the acm conference on information and knowledge management cikm pronounced sik m is an annual computer science research conference dedicated to information and knowledge management since the first event in 1992 the conference has evolved into one of the major forums for research on database management information retrieval and knowledge management 1 2 the conference is noted for its interdisciplinarity as it brings together communities that otherwise often publish at separate venues recent editions have attracted well beyond 500 participants 3 in addition to the main research program the conference also features a number of workshops tutorials and industry presentations 4 for many years the conference was held in the us since 2005 venues in other countries have been selected as well locations include 5 1992 baltimore md usa 1993 washington dc usa 1994 gaithersburg md usa 1995 baltimore md usa 1996 rockville md usa 1997 las vegas nv usa 1998 bethesda md usa 1999 kansas city mo usa 2000 washington dc usa 2001 atlanta ga usa 2002 mclean va usa 2003 new orleans la usa 2004 washington dc usa 2005 bremen germany 2006 arlington va usa 2007 lisbon portugal 6 2008 napa valley ca usa 7 2009 hong kong china 8 2010 toronto canada 9 2011 glasgow uk 10 edit see also sigir conference edit references official home page arnetminer ranking list www ir arnetminer http www arnetminer org page conference rank html www ir html retrieved 2011 06 11 cikm 2011 sponsorship page cikm 2011 home page dblp http www fc ul pt cikm2007 1 2 3 4 edit external links official home page 